tog-fancysig: Fuk iman̄-erieen̄ kire inu-nge-wiki (katap ugọbọ mgbọ yaage isi akpọk òsi-ikwaan̄ n̄a)
tog-enotifwatchlistpages: Ria imeelu jet emi mgbọ enwenebe akpọk mè ìre failu òkup me onineen̄-mkpọ n̄a
tog-enotifusertalkpages: Ria imeelu jet emi mgbọ enwenebe akpọk itumu-ikọ n̄a
tog-enotifminoredits: Ria imeelu si jet emi mgbọ ofolek asabọn nnen̄e-nge eyi akpọk mè failu
tog-enotifrevealaddr: Chili iman̄ imeelu n̄a jeen̄ me imeelu òkinyi ulook
tog-editsectiononrightclick: Rọ inyi ikọt inen̄e igesa me ikekeme ichip ulom me lek ibot ikọ
tog-editondblclick: Nen̄e akpọk sa me ikekeme mgbọ iba
tog-minordefault: Tap iman̄ ibe otutuuk nnen̄e-nge ìre asabọn me òkpọọn̄
tog-forceeditsummary: Rọ inyi ǹriọọn̄ mgbọ ǹkage nkana-ngwook nnen̄e-nsun̄ (mè ìre òkpọọn̄ nkana-ngwook eyi igwugwu irọ)
tog-useeditwarning: Rọ inyi ǹriọọn̄ mgbọ mbatele inu nkige me ǹkanyi esun̄
tog-previewonfirst: Jeen̄ ike-ibokup mgbọ ebenebe ikinen̄e ige
tog-uselivepreview: Jeen̄ ike-ibokup me ekakpọkge ìbọkọ akpọk ayaya
tog-usenewrc: Gbaan̄ unwene sun̄ me ọgbọn̄ gọọk me akpọk me unwene eyi mgburudun̄ mè onineen̄-mkpọ
tog-hideminor: Let asabọn nnen̄e-nge san̄a me unwene echi mgburudun̄
tog-hidepatrolled: Let nnen̄e-nge echi esàan̄be san̄a me unwene echi mgburudun̄
tog-newpageshidepatrolled: Let akpọk esàan̄be san̄a me onineen̄ ebi kè aya akpọk
tog-extendwatchlist: Chak onineen̄-mkpọ wele inyi ijeen̄ otutuuk unwene, ìkare gaalek echi ìrere ayaya ichit
tog-watchlisthideminor: Let asabọn nnen̄e-nsun̄ san̄a me onineen̄-mkpọ
tog-watchlisthidebots: Let nnen̄e-nsun̄ eyi bột san̄a me onineen̄-mkpọ
tog-watchlisthideown: Let nnen̄e-nsun̄ n̄a san̄a me onineen̄-mkpọ
tog-watchlisthideliu: Let nnen̄e-nsun̄ eyi ebi òsikwaan̄ ìtitibi inin̄ san̄a me onineen̄-mkpọ
tog-watchdefault: Tap akpọk mè failu nnen̄ebe ige sọ̀kọ me onineen̄-mkpọ n̄a
tog-watchmoves: Tap akpọk mè failu nnwenebe erieen̄ sọ̀kọ me onineen̄-mkpọ n̄a
tog-watchdeletion: Tap akpọk mè failu nchọkbe sọ̀kọ me onineen̄-mkpọ n̄a
tog-watchcreations: Tap otutuuk akpọk nchilibe mè failu nriabe sọ̀kọ me onineen̄-mkpọ n̄a
tog-watchuploads: Tap failu nriabe sọ̀kọ me onineen̄-mkpọ n̄a
tog-watchrollback: Tap akpọk echi nrọbe ngwu-nsun̄ sọ̀kọ me onineen̄-mkpọ n̄a
